(411, 1, '2013-09-23 10:16:55', '2013-09-23 10:16:55', '<div style="font-family: Tahoma, ''sans-sarif''; font-size: 14px; line-height: 27px;">\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Terms of Use</b>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDate Last Updated: September 26, 2013\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThis Agreement sets forth the terms and conditions that apply to your access and use of the Internet Web site located at www.marginmentor ("Margin Mentor"), as owned and operated by Margin Mentor (Pty) Ltd, on behalf of those of its direct or indirect subsidiaries and/or affiliates, (collectively referred to as “Margin Mentor”). By using Margin Mentor you agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of this Agreement and Margin Mentor’s Privacy and Security Policy, as they may be amended from time to time in the future (see “Modifications” below).\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Accepting the Terms</li>\r\n	<li>Privacy and your Personal Information</li>\r\n	<li>Description of the Service</li>\r\n	<li>Margin Mentor Offers and Third-Party Links</li>\r\n	<li>Your Registration Information</li>\r\n	<li>Your Use of the Service</li>\r\n	<li>Use With Your Mobile Device</li>\r\n	<li>Online and Mobile Alerts</li>\r\n	<li>Rights You Grant to Us</li>\r\n	<li>Margin Mentor’s Intellectual Property Rights</li>\r\n	<li>Access and Interference</li>\r\n	<li>Rules for Posting</li>\r\n	<li>Social Media Sites</li>\r\n	<li>Disclaimer of Representations and Warranties</li>\r\n	<li>Not a Financial Planner, Broker or Tax Advisor</li>\r\n	<li>Alert Disclaimer</li>\r\n	<li>Limitations on Margin Mentor’s Liability</li>\r\n	<li>Your Indemnification of Margin Mentor</li>\r\n	<li>Ending your relationship with Margin Mentor</li>\r\n	<li>Modifications</li>\r\n	<li>Governing Law and Forum for Disputes</li>\r\n	<li>Miscellaneous</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>1. Accepting the Terms</b>\r\n\r\nBy using the information, tools, software, features and functionality including content, updates and new releases located on Margin Mentor (together the “Service”), you agree to be bound by this Agreement, whether you are a “Visitor” (which means that you simply browse the Margin Mentor website) or you are a “Member” (which means that you have registered with Margin Mentor). The term “you” or “User” refers to a Visitor or a Member. The term “we” refers to Margin Mentor. If you wish to become a Member, communicate with other Members and make use of the Service, you must read this Agreement and indicate your acceptance during the Registration process.\r\n\r\nYou may not use the Service and you may not accept this Agreement if you are not of a legal age to form a binding contract with Margin Mentor.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you accept this Agreement, you represent that you have the capacity to be bound by it or if you are acting on behalf of a company or entity that you have the authority to bind such entity. Before you continue, you should print or save a local copy of this Agreement for your records.\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>2. Privacy and your Personal Information</b>\r\n\r\nFor information about Margin Mentor’s data protection practices, please read Margin Mentor Privacy and Security Policy, which is hereby incorporated into this Agreement. This policy explains how Margin Mentor treats your personal information when you access Margin Mentor and use the Service. The policy may be updated from time to time at our discretion. Changes will be effective upon posting to the site.\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>3. Description of the Service</b>\r\n\r\nThe Service is a business finance information management service that allows Members to consolidate and track their financial information on Margin Mentor. Based on such information, the Service may also present information relating to third party products or services (“Margin Mentor Offers”).\r\n\r\nThe Service is provided to you by Margin Mentor for a prescribed fee and is meant as an aid to assist you in organizing and managing your finances. It is not intended to provide legal, tax or financial advice.\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>4. Margin Mentor Offers and Third-Party Links</b>\r\n\r\nSome parts of the Service are supported by sponsored links from advertisers and display Margin Mentor Offers that may be custom matched to you based on information stored in the Service, queries made through the Service or other information. We will always disclose when a particular Margin Mentor Offer is sponsored.\r\n\r\nIn connection with Margin Mentor Offers, the Service will provide links to other web sites belonging to Margin Mentor advertisers and other third parties. Margin Mentor does not endorse, warrant or guarantee the products or services available through the Margin Mentor Offers (or any other third-party products or services advertised on or linked from our site), whether or not sponsored, and Margin Mentor is not an agent or broker or otherwise responsible for the activities or policies of those web sites. Margin Mentor does not guarantee that the loan, investment, plan or other service terms, rates or rewards offered by any particular advertiser or other third party on Margin Mentor are actually the terms that may be offered to you if you pursue the offer or that they are the best terms or lowest rates available in the market.\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>5. Your Registration Information</b>\r\n\r\nYou agree and understand that you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password which, together with your Login ID e-mail address, allows you to access the Service. That Login ID and password, together with any mobile number or other contact information you provide form your “Registration Information.”\r\n\r\nBy providing us with your e-mail address, you agree to receive all required notices electronically