 to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>9. Rights You Grant to Us</b>\r\n\r\nBy submitting information, data, passwords, usernames, PINs, other log-in information, materials and other content to Margin Mentor through the Service, you are licensing that content to Margin Mentor solely for the purpose of providing the Service. Margin Mentor may use and store the content, but only to provide the Service to you. By submitting this content to Margin Mentor, you represent that you are entitled to submit it to Margin Mentor for use for this purpose, without any obligation by Margin Mentor to pay any fees or other limitations.\r\n\r\nBy using the Service, you expressly authorize Margin Mentor to access your Account Information maintained by identified third parties, on your behalf as your agent. When you use the “Add Accounts” feature of the Service, you will be directly connected to the website for the third party you have identified. Margin Mentor will submit information including usernames and passwords that you provide to log you into the site. You hereby authorize and permit Margin Mentor to use and store information submitted by you to the Service (such as account passwords and user names) to accomplish the foregoing and to configure the Service so that it is compatible with the third party sites for which you submit your information. For purposes of this Agreement and solely to provide the Account Information to you as part of the Service, you grant Margin Mentor a limited power of attorney, and appoint Margin Mentor as your attorney-in-fact and agent, to access third party sites, retrieve and use your information with the full power and authority to do and perform each thing necessary in connection with such activities, as you could do in person. YOU ACKNOWLEDGE AND AGREE THAT WHEN MARGIN MENTOR IS ACCESSING AND RETRIEVING ACCOUNT INFORMATION FROM THIRD PARTY SITES, MARGIN MENTOR IS ACTING AS YOUR AGENT, AND NOT AS THE AGENT OF OR ON BEHALF OF THE THIRD PARTY. You understand and agree that the Service is not sponsored or endorsed by any third parties accessible through the Service.\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top">Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>10. Margin Mentor’s Intellectual Property Rights</b>\r\n\r\nThe contents of Margin Mentor, including its “look and feel” (e.g., text, graphics, images, logos and button icons), photographs, editorial content, notices, software (including html-based computer programs) and other material are protected under both United States and other applicable copyright, trademark and other laws. The contents of Margin Mentor belong or are licensed to Margin Mentor or its software or content suppliers. Margin Mentor grants you the right to view and use Margin Mentor subject to these terms. You may download or print a copy of information provided on Margin Mentor for your personal, internal and non-commercial use only. Any distribution, reprint or electronic reproduction of any content from Margin Mentor in whole or in part for any other purpose is expressly prohibited without our prior written consent.\r\n<p align="right"><b>Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>11. Access and Interference</b>\r\n\r\nYou agree that you will not:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Use any robot, spider, scraper, deep link or other similar automated data gathering or extraction tools, program, algorithm or methodology to access, acquire, copy or monitor Margin Mentor or any portion of Margin Mentor, without Margin Mentor’s express written consent, which may be withheld in Margin Mentor’s sole discretion;</li>\r\n	<li>Use or attempt to use any engine, software, tool, agent, or other device or mechanism (including without limitation browsers, spiders, robots, avatars or intelligent agents) to navigate or search Margin Mentor, other than the search engines and search agents available through the Service and other than generally available third-party web browsers (such as Microsoft Explorer);</li>\r\n	<li>Post or transmit any file which contains viruses, worms, Trojan horses or any other contaminating or destructive features, or that otherwise interfere with the proper working of Margin Mentor or the Service; or</li>\r\n	<li>Attempt to decipher, decompile, disassemble, or reverse-engineer any of the software comprising or in any way making up a part of Margin Mentor or the Service.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p align="right"><b class="back-to-top" >Back to Top</b></p>\r\n<b>12. Rules for Posting</b>\r\n\r\nAs part of the Service, Margin Mentor allows Members to post content on bulletin boards, blogs and at various other publicly available locations on Margin Mentor. These forums may be hosted by Margin Mentor or by one of our third party service providers on Margin Mentor’s behalf. You agree in posting content to follow certain rules.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You are responsible for all content you submit to Margin Mentor.</li>\r\n	<li>By submitting content to us, you represent that you have all necessary rights and hereby grant us a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free, sub licensable and transferable license to use, reproduce, distribute, prepare derivative works of, modify, display, and perform all or any portion of the content in connection with Margin Mentor and our business, including without limitation for promoting and redistributing part or all of the site (and derivative works thereof) in any media formats and through any media channels. You also hereby grant each User a non-exclusive license to access your posted content through Margin Mentor, and to use, reproduce, distribute, prepare derivative works of, display and perform such content as permitted through the functionality of Margin Mentor and under this Agreement.</li>\r\n	<li>You may not post or transmit any message which is libellous or defamatory, or which discloses private or personal matters concerning any person. You may not post or transmit any message, data, image or program that is indecent, obscene, pornographic, harassing, threatening, abusive, hateful, raci